data.description: Stanley Martin Company is now building energy-efficient homes in the master planned, Sage Creek community. The Pinewood plan is 4 beds, 2.5 baths in 2431 hsf. This plan offers a long list of features including cased windows, stained cabinets, granite in kitchen & baths, Samsung appliances, expandable smart devices, Honeywell programmable thermostat & Schlage front door lock that can be controlled from anywhere, Low-EPella energy savings windows, upgraded insulation, advanced air & moisture sealing, tankless water heater, radiant barrier sheathing, water-saving faucets, Co2 detectors, 30 year architectural shingles, gutters, insulated carriage style garage door w/ auto opener, floodlights & so much more! To learn more about the award winning Stanley Martin Company, stop by our model home located at 1182 Sapphire Dr, and don't forget to ask about the 100% financing and current incentives! Photos are of like model - Under Construction- Ready 01/2021.
